'''薩姆納·拜倫·邁爾斯'''（{{lang|en|'''Sumner Byron Myers'''}}，{{bd|1910年||1955年|catIdx=M}}），[[美國|美國]][[數學家|數學家]]，專長[[拓撲學|拓撲學]]。他在[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]跟隨[[馬斯頓·莫爾斯|馬斯頓·莫爾斯]]學習<ref name="inter">Tucker, A: ''[http://libweb.princeton.edu/libraries/firestone/rbsc/finding_aids/mathoral/pmc33.htm Interview with Albert Tucker] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070623191101/http://libweb.princeton.edu/libraries/firestone/rbsc/finding_aids/mathoral/pmc33.htm |date=2007-06-23 }}'', Princeton University, July 11, 1984. Last accessed December 5, 2005.</ref>，1932年博士畢業<ref name="grad">Mathematics Genealogy Project: ''[http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/html/id.phtml?id=7746 Sumner Byron Myers] {{Wayback|url=http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/html/id.phtml?id=7746 |date=20060902133351 }}'', no date. Last accessed December 5, 2005.</ref>。自1934年到1936年他在[[普林斯頓大學|普林斯頓大學]]當博士後<ref name="members">Princeton University: ''[http://www.math.ias.edu/mnames.html Members of the School of Mathematics] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20001213114100/http://www.math.ias.edu/mnames.html |date=2000-12-13 }}'', no date. Last accessed December 5, 2005.</ref>，然後在[[密歇根大學|密歇根大學]]任教授。該校有一個以他命名的優秀學生獎項<ref name="award">University of Michigan: ''[http://www.math.lsa.umich.edu/undergrad/Sumner%20Myers.pdf Sumner Myers Award] {{Wayback|url=http://www.math.lsa.umich.edu/undergrad/Sumner%20Myers.pdf |date=20041014075530 }}'', no date. Last accessed December 5, 2005.</ref>。他在一場足球賽中突然心臟病發逝世<ref name="death">Fisher, G.: ''[http://sunsite.utk.edu/math_archives/.http/hypermail/historia/aug99/0064.html (E-mail message)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070322155504/http://sunsite.utk.edu/math_archives/.http/hypermail/historia/aug99/0064.html |date=2007-03-22 }}'', August 7, 1999. Last accessed December 5, 2005.</ref>。

